WEBVTT

00:00:27.719 --> 00:00:30.440
My popcorn didn't kill a deaf man like me

00:00:30.559 --> 00:00:31.440
Uncle

00:00:31.839 --> 00:00:33.520
Uncle, you can't have this, Uncle

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:34.560
He

00:00:35.119 --> 00:00:36.640
...has a heart condition

00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:38.280
Even if you don't pop it

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:40.920
...he's gonna croak when his time comes

00:00:41.119 --> 00:00:41.600
Croak

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:42.759
Uncle

00:00:42.759 --> 00:00:43.719
Li Wai, you handle this

00:00:46.399 --> 00:00:47.079
This old man...

00:00:49.679 --> 00:00:51.799
...even without the bang, his time is up

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:52.679
Croak

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:54.799
Wasn't it supposed to be today?

00:00:56.039 --> 00:00:57.039
He was gone yesterday

00:00:57.039 --> 00:00:58.359
Why was it a day early?

00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:00.320
These aliens are so unreliable

00:01:01.399 --> 00:01:02.600
Xiaocan went quickly

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:03.799
He didn't suffer much

00:01:05.319 --> 00:01:07.200
Xiaocan didn't even speak to Guifang at the end

00:01:07.319 --> 00:01:09.519
Yeah, if only we hadn't moved

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:11.920
Where is Xiaocan?

00:01:13.120 --> 00:01:14.239
No one's here. Where's Fang'er?

00:01:14.719 --> 00:01:16.359
Hello, hello. I wanted to ask...

00:01:16.599 --> 00:01:18.439
...about Kong Xiaocan's memorial service

00:01:18.439 --> 00:01:19.079
Is it being held here?

00:01:19.159 --> 00:01:19.799
Kong Xiaocan?

00:01:20.319 --> 00:01:21.000
There is no funeral

00:01:21.239 --> 00:01:22.159
He's already been cremated

00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:24.640
Cremated?

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:26.439
Right, right. Go take a look in the back

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.200
Let's go, let's go

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:28.680
Thank you

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:29.280
Thanks

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:33.560
This...

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:46.319
Xurui, this is...

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:48.640
She is Guifang.

00:01:51.879 --> 00:01:52.879
Guifang.

00:01:52.959 --> 00:01:53.319
Fang'er.

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:53.920
Fang'er.

00:01:54.359 --> 00:01:55.640
You guys go to the cemetery first.

00:01:56.359 --> 00:01:58.120
I want to be alone with Xiaocan for a while.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:04.920
Now that Xiaocan is gone...

00:02:05.879 --> 00:02:07.359
Why has Guifang become old?

00:02:07.480 --> 00:02:08.400
Yeah.

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:09.120
It's so strange.

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:10.039
Why is that?

00:02:10.199 --> 00:02:12.280
I saw her like this at home once before.

00:02:12.719 --> 00:02:13.960
You saw it?

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:14.919
When did you see it?

00:02:14.919 --> 00:02:17.159
Because I didn't know what was going on back then.

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:19.280
Do you think it might be the alien?

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.280
Did he breach the contract?

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:21.639
Does breaching it make you old?

00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:22.599
I don't think so.

00:02:22.599 --> 00:02:23.879
This alien is so unreliable.

00:02:23.879 --> 00:02:24.520
It's terrifying.

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:25.360
What are you doing?

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:26.599
What are you guys doing?

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:31.199
Today is Xiaocan's funeral.

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:34.439
Godmother suddenly became old.

00:02:34.759 --> 00:02:36.439
It is indeed very strange.

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:40.159
But today is the day Xiaocan is buried.

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:43.800
Can't you show him some respect?

00:02:45.199 --> 00:02:46.319
Sorry, sorry, sorry.

00:02:48.719 --> 00:02:50.199
Xiaocan told me before he died...

00:02:51.159 --> 00:02:52.240
that his wish was...

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:56.479
to die amidst a display of brilliant fireworks.

00:02:58.719 --> 00:02:59.319
However...

00:03:00.759 --> 00:03:03.599
he died amidst fragrant popcorn instead.

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:08.199
I guess that counts as fulfilling his wish.

00:03:13.639 --> 00:03:14.280
In here...

00:03:15.520 --> 00:03:16.039
are...

00:03:17.159 --> 00:03:18.199
before Xiaocan died...

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:20.960
the videos I recorded for him.

00:03:25.159 --> 00:03:25.719
They are all...

00:03:26.599 --> 00:03:28.560
some heartfelt words he wanted to say to you.

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:30.960
Take a look.

00:03:40.039 --> 00:03:40.759
There's no sound.

00:03:41.159 --> 00:03:42.439
What? No sound?

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.879
It had sound when I recorded it.

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:47.159
Go fix it before we watch.

00:03:49.479 --> 00:03:50.479
I think regarding this matter...

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.759
something must be wrong with Guifang.

00:03:52.759 --> 00:03:53.759
What kind of problem?

00:03:53.759 --> 00:03:54.199
Yeah.

00:03:54.439 --> 00:03:55.560
Whether there's a problem...

00:03:56.639 --> 00:03:58.199
we'll know if we call A Fu over and ask.

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:01.159
I'm right here.

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:02.199
You humans...

00:04:02.199 --> 00:04:03.639
are you all this petty?

00:04:03.639 --> 00:04:04.159
This is the alien.

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:04.639
Yes.

00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:05.840
He doesn't look any different.

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:06.680
Let me ask you.

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:08.759
Why did Guifang become like this?

00:04:08.759 --> 00:04:10.080
Kong Guifang's aging...

00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:11.280
has nothing to do with us.

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:12.840
Simply put...

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:14.199
it is because she...

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:16.000
wants to commit suicide.

00:04:24.839 --> 00:04:25.759
Suicide?

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:26.160
What?

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:26.600
How is that possible?

00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:28.199
How could Guifang want to commit suicide? Sui...

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:32.319
The line is busy.

00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:32.920
Pick up!

00:04:32.920 --> 00:04:33.480
I can't get through.

00:04:33.480 --> 00:04:34.079
Why is there no sound?

00:04:34.319 --> 00:04:35.800
If we all call at once, of course it's busy!

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:36.720
You guys hang up, let me do it.

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:37.600
Right, right, right.

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:40.560
Fang'er contacted me.

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:41.639
But she said...

00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:43.800
there are still two outfits at the dry cleaner's.

00:04:44.040 --> 00:04:45.759
And don't forget the new warehouse's electricity bill.

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:46.519
Godmother...

00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:49.000
gave me the duck intestine recipe.

00:04:49.399 --> 00:04:51.000
She told me her school network password.

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:52.240
She asked me to monitor her experiment.

00:04:52.519 --> 00:04:53.759
Her experiment design is scheduled until...

00:04:54.439 --> 00:04:56.480
ne... next March.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:04.519
A Fu.

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:05.240
Where did she go?

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:06.879
I'll give you one day of life energy.

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:08.000
You tell me...

00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:09.439
where Guifang is right now.

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:11.279
Forget about the life energy.

00:05:12.399 --> 00:05:13.759
She is currently on her way...

00:05:14.319 --> 00:05:15.279
to the snow mountain.

00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:17.079
The snow mountain?

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:28.839
What do we do? Godmother still isn't picking up.

00:05:28.839 --> 00:05:29.839
Keep calling, keep calling!

00:05:40.839 --> 00:05:41.319
Hello, hello.

00:05:41.439 --> 00:05:42.199
Help me check someone.

00:05:43.040 --> 00:05:43.480
Yes, yes, yes.

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:45.519
Come on, quick.

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:47.279
Let me ask.

00:05:47.279 --> 00:05:47.720
Help me check this.

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:48.600
Have you seen this person?

00:05:51.079 --> 00:05:52.399
We haven't found anything here.

00:05:54.759 --> 00:05:55.759
No news from the police station either.

00:06:03.959 --> 00:06:05.800
Sister Liu, any news?

00:06:07.839 --> 00:06:08.600
Okay, thanks.

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:11.480
Hello.

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:12.959
Please keep an eye out for this person for us.

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:13.680
Call us.

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:14.759
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.079
The police station said...

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:29.319
The victim found today...

00:06:29.839 --> 00:06:30.680
Was a male.

00:06:31.639 --> 00:06:33.160
But no news about Auntie...

00:06:33.600 --> 00:06:34.639
Is good news.

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:37.519
Missing for over forty-eight hours...

00:06:37.519 --> 00:06:38.600
A case can be filed.

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:41.319
If Fang'er...

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:43.360
I'm saying if...

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:45.279
In case something happens...

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:47.920
She and Xiaocan have no other relatives left.

00:06:49.279 --> 00:06:51.319
Are we the only ones for the funeral?

00:06:51.800 --> 00:06:52.360
Of course.

00:06:53.519 --> 00:06:54.279
We are all family.

00:07:07.199 --> 00:07:08.199
Tying shoelaces like that...

00:07:08.879 --> 00:07:09.879
There's only one person.

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:16.560
Godmother.

00:07:39.600 --> 00:07:42.600
You guys even printed these missing person flyers in color.

00:07:43.079 --> 00:07:43.879
Waste of money.

00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:46.720
People have destination weddings.

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:50.120
Can't I hold a destination funeral for my son?

00:07:51.040 --> 00:07:51.600
Well, at least...

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:53.279
You should have told us before leaving, Fang'er.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:54.079
Yeah.

00:07:54.079 --> 00:07:54.959
We were so worried.

00:07:54.959 --> 00:07:56.399
Godmother, you just left like that, we...

00:07:58.160 --> 00:07:59.240
This was Xiaocan's wish.

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:00.040
Look.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.680
This is a message he didn't send out before.

00:08:03.519 --> 00:08:04.000
Buddy.

00:08:04.879 --> 00:08:06.279
Don't hold a chaotic funeral.

00:08:07.079 --> 00:08:08.120
I know you guys mean well.

00:08:08.959 --> 00:08:10.120
But I'm afraid my mom can't take it.

00:08:12.319 --> 00:08:14.120
You've been mentally preparing for so long.

00:08:14.639 --> 00:08:16.600
No need to say goodbye to the body anymore.

00:08:17.560 --> 00:08:19.199
Burn it, bury it, quickly.

00:08:19.600 --> 00:08:20.480
Let my mom turn the page.

00:08:21.439 --> 00:08:22.759
My life ends here, buddy.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:25.000
Sorry to trouble you guys from now on.

00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:26.759
Guifang.

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:29.120
Xiaocan wanted us to take care of your feelings.

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:31.279
Not for you to take care of ours.

00:08:31.319 --> 00:08:31.959
Exactly.

00:08:31.959 --> 00:08:33.159
Yeah, Godmother.

00:08:33.200 --> 00:08:35.080
You left without a word.

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:36.519
And didn't answer our calls.

00:08:36.679 --> 00:08:37.759
Given your current situation...

00:08:37.759 --> 00:08:38.559
We all thought you...

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:39.759
What situation?

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:44.320
I sent you messages.

00:08:45.279 --> 00:08:46.399
I arranged what needed arranging.

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:47.679
I asked for leave where needed.

00:08:48.399 --> 00:08:49.159
I didn't miss anything.

00:08:49.519 --> 00:08:50.919
You missed a lot.

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.519
A new seed project in your tech group...

00:08:52.519 --> 00:08:53.799
Was bought out by a company as a package.

00:08:54.279 --> 00:08:56.039
Professor Wang wanted to send you to guide it.

00:08:56.399 --> 00:08:57.919
It could have added a lot of points for your direct PhD.

00:08:58.840 --> 00:09:00.240
Nothing matters except life and death.

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:01.960
Come on, eat.

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:04.080
Guifang.

00:09:04.679 --> 00:09:05.840
The days ahead are still long.

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:06.679
Long.

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:08.440
These duck intestines...

00:09:08.639 --> 00:09:10.080
I can still only eat the ones you make.

00:09:10.519 --> 00:09:11.360
I don't want the secret recipe.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.279
I just want Guifang.

00:09:12.559 --> 00:09:13.440
You're crazy.

00:09:13.919 --> 00:09:14.320
Godmother.

00:09:14.759 --> 00:09:15.279
Look.

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:16.240
Since we're already here.

00:09:16.519 --> 00:09:17.200
Let's treat it as a trip.

00:09:17.519 --> 00:09:18.679
If we're happy, let's just hang out here.

00:09:19.639 --> 00:09:20.240
This message...

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:21.799
Was edited while waiting for popcorn.

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:24.039
Could it be...

00:09:24.600 --> 00:09:26.480
Xiaocan knew the time was moved up?

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.240
Did Xiaocan...

00:09:31.240 --> 00:09:32.799
Not want to face the final goodbye?

00:09:43.639 --> 00:09:44.080
Alright

00:09:44.879 --> 00:09:45.679
As the widow

00:09:45.840 --> 00:09:46.559
I'll say a few words

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:48.360
Since everyone is here

00:09:49.320 --> 00:09:50.440
Then let us, for Guifang,

00:09:50.799 --> 00:09:52.879
complete Xiaocan's traveling funeral

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:54.399
From this day on

00:09:54.879 --> 00:09:57.720
Kong Xiaocan's Traveling Funeral Troupe is officially established

00:09:58.320 --> 00:09:59.919
We set off tomorrow morning at ten

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:01.440
Cheers

00:10:02.559 --> 00:10:03.120
Cheers

00:10:04.080 --> 00:10:04.559
Cheers

00:10:09.279 --> 00:10:11.000
What are we going to do about Fang'er?

00:10:11.399 --> 00:10:12.559
We have to think of a way

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:13.919
to give her the will to live

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:15.759
We must stay by her side

00:10:16.080 --> 00:10:18.399
Maybe fulfilling the travel wish will help

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.399
What can I do for her?

00:10:21.039 --> 00:10:22.200
Eat up, the food is getting cold

00:10:23.399 --> 00:10:24.679
Eat, eat. Come on.

00:11:04.399 --> 00:11:05.840
I'm done. You guys take your time

00:11:06.799 --> 00:11:07.600
I'm done too. I'm done too

00:11:14.320 --> 00:11:14.840
Keep eating

00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:20.159
Eat

00:11:25.159 --> 00:11:25.559
How is it?

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:27.399
Was he this tall?

00:11:27.919 --> 00:11:28.960
I'm on my tiptoes. How about now?

00:11:31.480 --> 00:11:31.879
Brother

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:33.039
Is this okay?

00:11:33.759 --> 00:11:34.720
You can't see. Here, hold it like this

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:38.799
Here

00:11:40.879 --> 00:11:41.360
Brother

00:11:41.879 --> 00:11:42.240
Look

00:11:42.679 --> 00:11:44.039
We're back at this big snowy mountain

00:11:44.399 --> 00:11:46.080
You knew he skipped class to come to the snow mountain?

00:11:46.159 --> 00:11:47.840
Godmother, I didn't know he was...

00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:49.240
He lied to you. Alright, alright, it's okay

00:11:50.200 --> 00:11:51.200
Let's take a picture together

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:51.840
Okay, okay

00:11:53.279 --> 00:11:53.759
Miss

00:11:54.480 --> 00:11:55.440
Could you take a picture for us?

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:55.879
Sure, sure

00:11:55.879 --> 00:11:56.679
Okay, thanks. Thanks

00:11:56.879 --> 00:11:57.320
Just a moment

00:11:57.799 --> 00:11:58.080
Ready

00:11:58.279 --> 00:11:58.559
Ready

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:00.279
Ready

00:12:01.879 --> 00:12:02.759
Come on, look here

00:12:03.480 --> 00:12:04.720
One, two, three

00:12:06.120 --> 00:12:06.840
One more

00:12:07.399 --> 00:12:08.679
One, two, three

00:12:29.320 --> 00:12:29.720
Hello

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:31.000
Your son is really handsome

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:32.039
The mom is quite young too

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:37.120
She's not my mom

00:12:39.960 --> 00:12:40.919
She's the person I care about most

00:12:50.960 --> 00:12:51.399
Guifang

00:12:52.120 --> 00:12:52.759
I know right now

00:12:52.759 --> 00:12:53.919
you're in no mood to listen to this

00:12:54.399 --> 00:12:56.000
but these past few days, I've realized

00:12:56.559 --> 00:12:57.480
no matter what you look like,

00:12:57.480 --> 00:12:58.879
my feelings for you remain the same.

00:12:59.559 --> 00:13:00.440
As long as I'm by your side,

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:01.679
I get nervous.

00:13:02.320 --> 00:13:03.720
Whenever you look at me, I...

00:13:04.440 --> 00:13:05.320
I... I just want to run away.

00:13:07.399 --> 00:13:08.399
Are you that afraid of me?

00:13:08.639 --> 00:13:09.240
It's not fear.

00:13:09.519 --> 00:13:09.840
It's...

00:13:10.679 --> 00:13:11.480
it's that I care.

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:14.440
I'm not forcing you to accept me.

00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:16.879
I fully respect if you don't accept me.

00:13:17.679 --> 00:13:18.360
I just want to

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:20.120
tell you how I feel.

00:13:22.159 --> 00:13:22.919
Guifang.

00:13:24.039 --> 00:13:25.639
Your bravery and fearlessness have always inspired me.

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:26.759
Being by your side,

00:13:27.360 --> 00:13:28.720
I've become fearless just like you.

00:13:31.720 --> 00:13:33.240
How long did you spend memorizing those lines?

00:13:36.440 --> 00:13:37.320
Fearless?

00:13:38.879 --> 00:13:40.039
Because mothers are strong.

00:13:44.639 --> 00:13:45.120
Guifang.

00:13:45.919 --> 00:13:46.320
Fang'er.

00:13:46.639 --> 00:13:47.799
Professor Wang just called.

00:13:48.600 --> 00:13:50.559
There's a problem with the seedlings sold a few days ago.

00:13:50.679 --> 00:13:51.759
The two grad students sent to guide them

00:13:51.759 --> 00:13:52.600
can't solve it.

00:13:53.080 --> 00:13:54.200
There's a typhoon in Hainan right now.

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:55.360
Professor Wang is stuck there.

00:13:55.879 --> 00:13:56.679
Right now, other than her,

00:13:56.679 --> 00:13:57.960
you're the only one who understands the situation.

00:13:58.600 --> 00:13:59.879
If we delay another three or four days,

00:14:00.200 --> 00:14:01.519
millions worth of seedlings will be ruined.

00:14:09.639 --> 00:14:11.279
We've seen pretty much everything we came to see.

00:14:12.519 --> 00:14:13.200
Let's go back.

00:14:18.440 --> 00:14:19.679
Godmother is willing to go back with us.

00:14:20.320 --> 00:14:21.080
That's a good thing.

00:14:22.519 --> 00:14:24.000
Company isn't a cure-all.

00:14:25.039 --> 00:14:26.480
And traveling can't solve problems either.

00:14:27.320 --> 00:14:28.679
She hasn't turned young at all.

00:14:29.360 --> 00:14:29.960
This proves

00:14:30.879 --> 00:14:32.000
she still has no will to live.

00:14:36.360 --> 00:14:37.480
Let's think of another way then.

00:14:57.440 --> 00:14:58.080
A Fu, you...

00:15:05.200 --> 00:15:05.840
Xiaocan!

00:15:09.519 --> 00:15:10.080
Xiaocan!

00:15:15.320 --> 00:15:16.039
What's wrong? What's wrong?

00:15:16.039 --> 00:15:17.440
I just saw Xiaocan.

00:15:18.519 --> 00:15:19.600
He fell right from up there.

00:15:19.600 --> 00:15:21.320
And he... he shouted "A Fu".

00:15:21.799 --> 00:15:22.879
In the blink of an eye, he was gone.

00:15:22.960 --> 00:15:23.720
Where did he run off to?

00:15:23.799 --> 00:15:24.600
What's wrong? What's wrong, Godmother? Godmother?

00:15:24.639 --> 00:15:25.240
What happened? What happened?

00:15:25.240 --> 00:15:26.399
I just saw Xiaocan.

00:15:26.639 --> 00:15:27.840
He fell right from up there.

00:15:28.080 --> 00:15:29.320
And he shouted "A Fu".

00:15:29.600 --> 00:15:30.600
I... I don't know

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:32.000
how he just disappeared in the blink of an eye.

00:15:32.000 --> 00:15:32.720
Is it this one?

00:15:32.919 --> 00:15:33.679
Isn't he right here?

00:15:33.799 --> 00:15:34.840
Not me... not him.

00:15:34.840 --> 00:15:36.080
I really saw Xiaocan.

00:15:36.080 --> 00:15:36.360
Godmother.

00:15:36.440 --> 00:15:37.600
And he shouted "A Fu".

00:15:37.600 --> 00:15:38.480
Xiaocan isn't here anymore.

00:15:38.480 --> 00:15:39.080
What do you mean Xiaocan isn't here?

00:15:39.080 --> 00:15:39.840
Didn't you say he's gone?

00:15:39.840 --> 00:15:40.320
Don't worry.

00:15:40.320 --> 00:15:41.200
How could it not be him?

00:15:41.200 --> 00:15:42.159
I saw him with my own eyes.

00:15:42.159 --> 00:15:42.799
How could it not?

00:15:42.799 --> 00:15:44.279
How is it not him? Godmother, calm down.

00:15:44.279 --> 00:15:45.039
Xiaocan is no longer here.

00:15:45.039 --> 00:15:45.960
Don't you already know that?

00:15:45.960 --> 00:15:46.879
You know he's gone.

00:15:46.879 --> 00:15:47.320
That's right.

00:15:47.799 --> 00:15:48.879
I can't explain it to you.

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:50.480
Fang'er... Godmother...

00:15:51.399 --> 00:15:51.720
Godmother.

00:15:51.720 --> 00:15:52.759
Get away, get away!

00:15:52.759 --> 00:15:53.759
Stop bothering me!

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:56.320
Sister Rui, can you still contact that A Fu?

00:15:56.679 --> 00:15:58.759
I haven't been able to find him since the funeral.

00:15:58.759 --> 00:16:00.240
Ma Jianfei, pick up, pick up.

00:16:00.639 --> 00:16:02.360
Ma Jianfei, Ma Jianfei, pick up the phone.

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:04.440
I really just saw him.

00:16:05.159 --> 00:16:06.600
He fell right from up there.

00:16:07.240 --> 00:16:09.080
Why can't any of you hear it?

00:17:54.559 --> 00:17:54.960
Guifang

00:17:54.960 --> 00:17:55.519
Who is that?

00:17:55.799 --> 00:17:57.759
It seems to be Godmother's former colleague, Auntie Niu.

00:17:57.759 --> 00:17:58.880
It really is you.

00:17:58.920 --> 00:17:59.799
Auntie Niu, hello.

00:18:00.079 --> 00:18:01.519
Long time no see.

00:18:03.160 --> 00:18:04.400
How is your illness?

00:18:05.720 --> 00:18:07.000
I'm fully recovered.

00:18:07.079 --> 00:18:08.200
Fully recovered.

00:18:09.079 --> 00:18:11.119
You had pancreatic cancer.

00:18:13.240 --> 00:18:14.279
Your son is capable.

00:18:15.279 --> 00:18:17.920
Right, right, right. You raised a good son.

00:18:18.559 --> 00:18:20.279
I said so back then.

00:18:20.480 --> 00:18:22.160
Xiaocan is promising.

00:18:22.240 --> 00:18:24.039
He'll definitely have a great future.

00:18:24.039 --> 00:18:26.519
Even though he didn't get to study in Belgium.

00:18:26.799 --> 00:18:28.519
But he cured your illness.

00:18:29.079 --> 00:18:29.839
That's great.

00:18:30.559 --> 00:18:31.119
Look at you now.

00:18:31.200 --> 00:18:32.599
You're younger than before.

00:18:32.720 --> 00:18:34.319
Like a career woman.

00:18:35.119 --> 00:18:35.680
That's great.

00:18:36.359 --> 00:18:37.440
How are you doing now?

00:18:37.920 --> 00:18:38.359
Me?

00:18:40.000 --> 00:18:41.039
Don't even ask about me.

00:18:41.519 --> 00:18:42.480
To tell you the truth.

00:18:42.920 --> 00:18:44.319
I have rectal cancer.

00:18:45.000 --> 00:18:45.960
But it's okay.

00:18:45.960 --> 00:18:47.000
It's still in the early stages.

00:18:47.240 --> 00:18:47.799
It's fine.

00:18:48.559 --> 00:18:51.119
I have no children and no partner in this life.

00:18:51.440 --> 00:18:53.119
I use the best medicine.

00:18:53.359 --> 00:18:55.039
I spend money freely.

00:18:55.240 --> 00:18:57.759
My biggest wish before I die...

00:18:58.599 --> 00:18:59.960
...is to live in a new house.

00:18:59.960 --> 00:19:00.359
Look.

00:19:01.039 --> 00:19:02.240
This is the new house I bought.

00:19:02.279 --> 00:19:04.519
120 square meters, large three-bedroom. It's wonderful.

00:19:04.680 --> 00:19:05.720
Come, let's go up and take a look.

00:19:06.359 --> 00:19:07.799
Maybe another day. I have things to do.

00:19:08.079 --> 00:19:09.039
What other day?

00:19:09.039 --> 00:19:10.880
How many more times can we meet?

00:19:11.119 --> 00:19:13.519
Another day means seeing me at the funeral.

00:19:13.839 --> 00:19:14.799
Come on, come on. Really.

00:19:15.079 --> 00:19:16.759
I really missed you.

00:19:16.839 --> 00:19:17.640
Missed you to death.

00:19:20.920 --> 00:19:21.640
Reporting in.

00:19:21.759 --> 00:19:22.640
Fang'er is safe now.

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:23.960
She went to Auntie Niu's house. Don't worry.

00:19:27.440 --> 00:19:27.920
It's right here.

00:19:28.519 --> 00:19:29.319
Number 02.

00:19:31.000 --> 00:19:31.480
Xiao Guan.

00:19:32.680 --> 00:19:33.400
Auntie Niu is here.

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:35.000
Bro, bro, bro, stop working, stop working.

00:19:35.400 --> 00:19:36.880
Don't hurt Auntie Niu and this sister.

00:19:37.039 --> 00:19:38.119
Let me introduce you.

00:19:38.359 --> 00:19:40.079
This is our contractor, Xiao Guan.

00:19:40.759 --> 00:19:42.279
This is my good friend.

00:19:42.599 --> 00:19:44.079
My closest sister.

00:19:44.440 --> 00:19:45.240
Sister, hello, hello.

00:19:45.440 --> 00:19:46.079
Call her Auntie.

00:19:47.279 --> 00:19:49.039
You're too young, Auntie.

00:19:49.160 --> 00:19:50.599
You've maintained yourself so well.

00:19:51.079 --> 00:19:51.400
Come.

00:19:51.519 --> 00:19:52.079
Look around.

00:19:52.119 --> 00:19:52.960
Feel free to look around.

00:19:52.960 --> 00:19:54.200
The wall putty is all done.

00:19:54.599 --> 00:19:56.480
The ceiling, the ceiling, the ceiling isn't done yet.

00:19:57.160 --> 00:19:59.319
Auntie Niu, living here alone will be very comfortable.

00:20:01.599 --> 00:20:02.359
The view is pretty good.

00:20:02.359 --> 00:20:03.359
You can even see the mountains.

00:20:04.599 --> 00:20:05.279
Let me tell you.

00:20:05.960 --> 00:20:08.279
As soon as I came here, I set my eyes on this unit.

00:20:08.279 --> 00:20:09.640
Auntie Niu has great taste.

00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:11.599
Look, surrounded by mountains on all sides.

00:20:12.079 --> 00:20:13.960
The breeze will be so cool at night.

00:20:14.200 --> 00:20:15.200
If you think the breeze isn't enough...

00:20:15.519 --> 00:20:16.799
...we'll install a fan here for you.

00:20:17.160 --> 00:20:18.680
360-degree circulation.

00:20:19.400 --> 00:20:20.799
When the time comes, make sure the tiles...

00:20:21.000 --> 00:20:22.079
...are done beautifully for me.

00:20:22.079 --> 00:20:22.440
Sure.

00:20:22.839 --> 00:20:23.400
Right here...

00:20:23.960 --> 00:20:25.200
...we'll put a small table.

00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:27.039
Eating sunflower seeds, chatting, how nice.

00:20:27.640 --> 00:20:29.200
So beautiful, I can picture it already.

00:20:30.119 --> 00:20:32.640
What's the estimated budget for this renovation?

00:20:33.480 --> 00:20:35.359
Including labor and materials, about 350,000.

00:20:35.920 --> 00:20:36.480
That expensive?

00:20:36.799 --> 00:20:37.799
Expensive? Not at all.

00:20:38.359 --> 00:20:39.599
This is a friendly price.

00:20:40.000 --> 00:20:41.880
I use big brands, good materials.

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:43.920
Auntie Niu, rest assured.

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:45.480
Every penny will be spent where it counts.

00:20:45.599 --> 00:20:46.640
Refund the excess, make up the shortage.

00:20:46.799 --> 00:20:47.480
No problem.

00:20:48.079 --> 00:20:49.039
Quite a few rooms.

00:20:51.319 --> 00:20:52.519
These are all big bay windows.

00:20:52.599 --> 00:20:53.039
Right.

00:20:53.279 --> 00:20:54.519
Pretty good. Bay windows are great.

00:20:54.519 --> 00:20:54.960
When it's done...

00:20:55.599 --> 00:20:56.960
...I'll save a room for you.

00:20:57.200 --> 00:20:58.680
You have to come stay here.

00:20:59.319 --> 00:21:00.119
Auntie is staying here too?

00:21:00.119 --> 00:21:00.920
Of course.

00:21:01.400 --> 00:21:03.240
Tell me what style you like then.

00:21:03.440 --> 00:21:04.759
I'll design it for you.

00:21:05.039 --> 00:21:05.920
It's all within the budget.

00:21:06.519 --> 00:21:07.880
Give some suggestions.

00:21:08.480 --> 00:21:11.240
Xiao Guan, bring your design blueprints...

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:13.279
...or the renderings for me to see.

00:21:13.440 --> 00:21:13.799
Don't have any.

00:21:15.039 --> 00:21:16.519
It's all in my head.

00:21:17.119 --> 00:21:18.440
Who needs design plans?

00:21:18.720 --> 00:21:20.720
I've already imagined the scene.

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:22.119
It's... it's all in my brain.

00:21:22.880 --> 00:21:24.359
You've got some nerve.

00:21:24.359 --> 00:21:25.519
You don't even have a design plan...

00:21:25.519 --> 00:21:27.400
...and you dare to start marking lines?

00:21:27.519 --> 00:21:29.000
Don't talk about that. Auntie Niu knows.

00:21:29.079 --> 00:21:31.599
I'm famous in the renovation world for my smart brain.

00:21:31.920 --> 00:21:32.519
Let me tell you.

00:21:32.519 --> 00:21:35.160
He's renovated over a dozen units in this building.

00:21:35.160 --> 00:21:36.000
Yes, don't mention it.

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:36.839
Apartments over 200 square meters...

00:21:36.839 --> 00:21:37.799
...I drew them all by hand.

00:21:37.920 --> 00:21:38.920
Then do you have the purchase list?

00:21:39.039 --> 00:21:39.400
No.

00:21:39.960 --> 00:21:41.319
It's all in my head.

00:21:41.720 --> 00:21:43.559
No purchase list?

00:21:43.880 --> 00:21:44.359
Purchase list...

00:21:44.640 --> 00:21:45.200
This brain...

00:21:45.279 --> 00:21:45.920
Yes, yes, yes.

00:21:45.920 --> 00:21:46.359
Wait a moment.

00:21:46.359 --> 00:21:47.920
How can you not have that?

00:21:51.119 --> 00:21:52.680
Of course there is, Auntie Niu.

00:21:53.480 --> 00:21:55.640
You have to remember the details.

00:21:55.640 --> 00:21:58.000
Don't worry, we've gone over all this.

00:21:58.720 --> 00:21:59.279
I'm telling you,

00:21:59.279 --> 00:22:00.720
when the time comes, the glue...

00:22:00.880 --> 00:22:02.359
has to be the best kind.

00:22:02.359 --> 00:22:03.559
Because otherwise I...

00:22:03.960 --> 00:22:04.440
Don't you worry.

00:22:04.440 --> 00:22:05.640
I'll use all natural stuff for you.

00:22:05.839 --> 00:22:06.480
It won't smell at all.

00:22:06.480 --> 00:22:07.680
Auntie Niu, no need to see me out.

00:22:08.799 --> 00:22:11.960
It's fine. I'm relieved to see you doing well.

00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:14.640
Come visit often when you're free.

00:22:14.759 --> 00:22:15.079
Okay.

00:22:15.240 --> 00:22:17.200
Treat this place like your own home.

00:22:17.640 --> 00:22:19.000
Okay. Take care of yourself.

00:22:19.559 --> 00:22:20.200
Okay, sure.

00:22:20.359 --> 00:22:20.839
Goodbye.

00:22:21.440 --> 00:22:22.079
Take care.

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:24.799
Bye.

00:22:30.880 --> 00:22:31.480
Auntie Niu.

00:22:33.920 --> 00:22:35.519
How about I oversee the renovation for you?

00:22:36.079 --> 00:22:36.880
No need for that.

00:22:37.519 --> 00:22:39.079
You've just recovered from a serious illness.

00:22:39.079 --> 00:22:40.480
You should just focus on resting.

00:22:40.640 --> 00:22:41.680
Don't be so polite with me.

00:22:42.519 --> 00:22:43.480
Just focus on your treatment.

00:22:44.559 --> 00:22:45.599
Nothing matters more than your life.

00:22:49.559 --> 00:22:49.920
Okay.

00:22:56.079 --> 00:22:57.680
We'll have to make do with this for now.

00:22:57.880 --> 00:22:58.920
Fang'er, you sleep on this.

00:22:59.680 --> 00:23:00.640
The pillow with the most flowers.

00:23:01.079 --> 00:23:02.759
This flowery quilt is yours too.

00:23:02.920 --> 00:23:03.359
Right.

00:23:29.960 --> 00:23:30.559
Time to get up.

00:23:31.359 --> 00:23:31.720
Hurry up.

00:23:32.000 --> 00:23:32.519
Xiao Yin.

00:23:33.000 --> 00:23:33.359
Xixi.

00:23:33.839 --> 00:23:34.640
Wake up, wake up.

00:23:42.519 --> 00:23:42.839
Fang'er.

00:23:44.119 --> 00:23:45.279
Come on, come on.

00:23:52.880 --> 00:23:53.640
These wires...

00:23:54.079 --> 00:23:55.839
we need to redesign them later.

00:23:56.279 --> 00:23:57.200
They can't be crossed like that.

00:23:57.200 --> 00:23:58.119
That would be very dangerous.

00:23:58.319 --> 00:23:58.839
Don't worry.

00:23:58.839 --> 00:23:59.640
It's all in my head.

00:23:59.960 --> 00:24:01.599
And the waterproofing for the kitchen and bathroom...

00:24:01.599 --> 00:24:02.559
we must apply a few extra layers.

00:24:02.559 --> 00:24:04.039
Leaking downstairs would be a huge hassle.

00:24:04.559 --> 00:24:05.519
It's all in my head.

00:24:05.799 --> 00:24:07.640
Should the floor heating go through the kitchen or the bathroom?

00:24:07.640 --> 00:24:08.720
We'll design that later.

00:24:08.720 --> 00:24:09.960
Over here, I want to put a...

00:24:09.960 --> 00:24:11.799
...floor-standing air conditioner for her.

00:24:12.079 --> 00:24:13.039
Wait, wait a sec, Sister.

00:24:13.759 --> 00:24:15.079
About that just now...

00:24:15.759 --> 00:24:17.160
how did you say the floor heating should go?

00:24:17.240 --> 00:24:17.880
I don't think I remembered it.

00:24:18.319 --> 00:24:19.640
Didn't you say your brain was good?

00:24:19.839 --> 00:24:22.240
Staying up late these days has made it a bit rusty.

00:24:22.240 --> 00:24:22.960
Floor heating.

00:24:23.680 --> 00:24:24.200
Fang'er.

00:24:24.200 --> 00:24:25.440
You're finally back.

00:24:25.720 --> 00:24:26.519
Godmother.

00:24:27.400 --> 00:24:29.319
You've worked hard, you've worked hard.

00:24:29.319 --> 00:24:30.839
Hard work, hard work, hard work.

00:24:31.680 --> 00:24:32.359
Sit down, sit down.

00:24:32.599 --> 00:24:34.000
You must be tired. Let me massage you.

00:24:34.359 --> 00:24:35.200
No, no.

00:24:35.319 --> 00:24:35.920
Are you hungry?

00:24:41.240 --> 00:24:42.559
I didn't want to go through a goodbye.

00:24:43.160 --> 00:24:45.160
So I didn't tell everyone I was going north.

00:24:47.839 --> 00:24:49.200
The plane is about to take off.

00:24:50.519 --> 00:24:52.839
A top-tier company sent me an offer.

00:24:54.039 --> 00:24:55.640
Don't worry about me, everyone.

00:25:01.920 --> 00:25:03.279
Make sure to take good care of yourselves.

00:25:06.319 --> 00:25:07.200
Let's eat, let's eat.

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:07.799
Auntie.

00:25:08.799 --> 00:25:09.880
You need to look forward too.

00:25:14.839 --> 00:25:15.880
I just got home.

00:25:16.119 --> 00:25:17.799
I'm downstairs waiting for the elevator.

00:25:18.000 --> 00:25:20.720
Lin Xurui, guess who I am? What are you doing?

00:25:20.839 --> 00:25:21.440
Li Wai.

00:25:21.440 --> 00:25:22.440
You're so annoying.

00:25:22.440 --> 00:25:22.960
Where's Guifang?

00:25:23.759 --> 00:25:25.279
Fang'er? Oh, right, she's preparing fruit.

00:25:25.440 --> 00:25:26.079
Godmother, Guifang.

00:25:26.359 --> 00:25:27.319
Come see Sister Rui. Sister Rui.

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:28.119
Yes.

00:25:30.559 --> 00:25:31.359
Xurui.

00:25:33.599 --> 00:25:34.920
Come, Auntie Niu, take a look.

00:25:36.640 --> 00:25:40.160
This... this is such a surprise! This...

00:25:40.359 --> 00:25:42.519
This island counter, it's marble.

00:25:42.960 --> 00:25:44.960
These cabinets, look, gold trim.

00:25:44.960 --> 00:25:45.920
There's no smell at all.

00:25:46.920 --> 00:25:48.799
It's metal. This is super sturdy.

00:25:49.079 --> 00:25:49.960
This sofa...

00:25:50.079 --> 00:25:51.279
Is this a gift from you?

00:25:51.440 --> 00:25:53.599
This is all within the budget.

00:25:54.599 --> 00:25:55.160
Auntie Niu.

00:25:55.480 --> 00:25:57.799
The tens of thousands we saved are in your card.

00:25:58.440 --> 00:26:00.039
What? You saved me tens of thousands?

00:26:00.119 --> 00:26:00.920
Of course.

00:26:01.480 --> 00:26:03.640
Auntie Fang's brain really works well.

00:26:03.920 --> 00:26:05.000
It's all in the head.

00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:07.880
Guifang, this is great. Come, come.

00:26:08.359 --> 00:26:09.319
Look at the balcony over here.

00:26:09.839 --> 00:26:10.640
You're amazing.

00:26:10.640 --> 00:26:10.960
Come.

00:26:11.839 --> 00:26:12.640
These tiles...

00:26:13.200 --> 00:26:13.759
So vibrant.

00:26:14.440 --> 00:26:15.799
Right? Didn't we talk about this back then?

00:26:15.880 --> 00:26:17.000
Put a small tea table here.

00:26:17.240 --> 00:26:17.839
Drink some tea.

00:26:18.559 --> 00:26:19.519
How beautiful. It looks so good.

00:26:19.519 --> 00:26:20.279
It looks so good.

00:26:20.720 --> 00:26:21.759
Guifang, look.

00:26:22.200 --> 00:26:22.519
This...

00:26:23.240 --> 00:26:25.319
We'll live together then.

